        {
            "title": "中國下周一起對原產美國部份商品加徵關稅 港股午後跟隨外圍升幅收窄",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國務院宣布，將於2月10日起對原產於美國的部份進口商品加徵關稅。港股午後也跟隨其他亞洲股市升幅收窄。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/China_Supply_Chain_Expo_24332553928573.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/China_Supply_Chain_Expo_24332553928573.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數午後升幅一度收窄至80點，低見20297點，其後升幅重新擴大，截至下午約1時17分，恒指報20465點，升247點或1.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14681399-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e4%b8%8b%e5%91%a8%e4%b8%80%e8%b5%b7%e5%b0%8d%e5%8e%9f%e7%94%a2%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e9%83%a8%e4%bb%bd%e5%95%86%e5%93%81%e5%8a%a0%e5%be%b5%e9%97%9c%e7%a8%85-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88",
